snippet.textDisplay: I guess I am a brunch bitch or a secret alcoholic lol because I am down for a Bloody Mary with a extra shot of Vodka lol with a lime or celery stick. I also like a tequila salt and lime, a alien shot, liquid marijuana, Brooklyn’s hard cider (a local bartenders mix drink it’s almost like a Long Island ice tea with vodka and whiskey and cranberry juice), I like a vodka blue raspberry sparkle (it has blue raspberries, pop rocks lined top, vodka or rum, with a lime and cranberry juice) I never have sugar added to my drinks I like the bitter sweet taste of the mix without the extra sugar and I always squeeze the limes and fruit into my drinks and keep the left overs in my drink to enhance how strong the bitter sourness lol I like bitter sour sweet like stuff. Believe it or another reason I don’t add sugar is the limes and lemons actually have more sugar than you think. A pound of strawberries has less sugar than a pound of lemons. It’s so acidic you can taste the sweetness. If I go and drink at a bar expect me to be there for 6-8 hours because I drink only liquor that’s white or red or brown liquor. I’m wine a drinker too lol. But I sip on my drinks I don’t drink to get drunk lol I drink to lay back relax and chill out. It takes me about 15-25 mins on a Bloody Mary. I typically drink a 1/2 and 1/2 sweet tea with lemon or lime on the side in between my drinks I take casual sips to stay a little sober but not too sober but not too drunk or tipsy but I will say in the matter of 6-8 hours I typically get 3-4 1/2 and 1/2 sweet tea with lemon or lime. But I drink about 12-16 more or less drinks that’s alcoholic lol I can’t drive I typically walk to the bar and back or have a ride lol so I don’t drink and drive I drink and ride lol I isn’t often I go drink lol but when I am down I’m down lol
